    "sections": [
      {
        "blocks": [
          {
            "inline": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "Draw random samples from a multivariate normal distribution."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Summary"
      },
      {
        "blocks": [
          {
            "inline": [
              {
                "kind": "text",
                "text": "The multivariate normal, multinormal or Gaussian distribution is a\ngeneralization of the one-dimensional normal distribution to higher\ndimensions.  Such a distribution is specified by its mean and\ncovariance matrix.  These parameters are analogous to the mean\n(average or \"center\") and variance (standard deviation, or \"width,\"\nsquared) of the one-dimensional normal distribution."
              }
            ],
            "type": "paragraph"
          },
          {
            "argument_inline": [],
            "content_blocks": [
              {
                "inline": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "New code should use the\n"
                  },
                  {
                    "external_url": "https://numpy.org/doc/stable/reference/generated/numpy.random.Generator.multivariate_normal.html",
                    "href": "",
                    "kind": "link",
                    "target": "random.Generator.multivariate_normal",
                    "text": "multivariate_normal"
                  },
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "\nmethod of a "
                  },
                  {
                    "external_url": "https://numpy.org/doc/stable/reference/generated/numpy.random.Generator.html",
                    "href": "",
                    "kind": "link",
                    "target": "random.Generator",
                    "text": "Generator"
                  },
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": " instance instead;\nplease see the "
                  },
                  {
                    "display_text": "random-quick-start",
                    "explicit_title": false,
                    "external_url": "https://numpy.org/doc/stable/reference/generated/numpy.random-quick-start.html",
                    "href": "",
                    "kind": "role_reference",
